Paper: hep-th/9807209

Date: 1998-07-28

Title: Black hole - D-brane correspondence

Authors: M. Bertolini, P. Fre, F. Hussain, R. Iengo, C. Nunez and C. Scrucca

Comments: 15 pages, LaTeX. Contribution by C. Nunez to the conference Quantum

Gravity in the Southern Cone, Bariloche 7-10 January 1998; to appear in theproceedingsJournal-ref: Int.J.Theor.Phys. 38 (1999) 1385-1397

We explore the connection between D-branes and black holes in one particular$D$-brane boundary state description we show the equivalence with a doubleextremal N=2 black hole solution of four dimensional supergravity.